              </svg>
              {lang === 'en' ? 'Code' : 'Código'}
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- EdgarCountryMadness -->
    <article class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 via-purple-50/30 to-gray-100 dark:from-gray-800 dark:via-purple-900/20 dark:to-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 p-6">
          <a href="https://edgarcountrymadness.netlify.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block">
            <img src="/img/countryMadness.webp" alt="EdgarCountryMadness project" 
                 class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:shadow-xl" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 p-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">EdgarCountryMadness</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 rounded text-xs">HTML</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 rounded text-xs">CSS</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 rounded text-xs">JavaScript</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            {lang === 'en'
              ? 'Page that shows information about countries and cities by consuming different APIs using JavaScript, also includes a mini-game to guess the flag.'
              : 'Página la cual muestra información de países y ciudades mediante el consumo de distintas APIs utilizando JavaScript, también incluye un minijuego de adivinar la bandera.'}
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="https://github.com/DemboNauta/edgarCountryMadness" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
               class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-100 text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gray-900/25 dark:hover:shadow-gray-100/25">
